featured_reviews.review_id:
A very beautiful Sunni Muslim Masjid, in the Takiya Ward Bhandara. It is in the center place of the Takiya Ward and well in reach for every one. All people are welcome here to offer prayers for five times every day. The committee is very good and taking care of all the amenities very well. Apart from the regular prayers the masjid is also taking care of wellbeing on poor and needy people in and around the vicinity. All the program of special events like Shab e Qdr, Shab e Meraj, etc are celebrated with all the peoples and naat and recitation of Quran is done for the whole night. Peoples are gathering here for offering the prayers here every day five times.
Nice place and good people taking care of everyone and everything here. Imam who performed the Namaz is very good and qirat is very beautiful. People love to listen him very often.
Nice place to perform Namaz.

 *When all the earnings of life are divided by death, the result is only that, wake up from the sleep of negligence and save something better for the eternal life of the hereafter*

Some people will also be used as fuel in hell. May Allah save us from such a horrible scene and save us from the fire of hell, which is many times hotter than the fire of this world.

*Overthinking kills happiness, fear kills courage, lying kills confidence, and doubt kills relationships.....*

* Muhammad Mubarak Ali Arriavi *
